description: Try our easy to follow Halloween Egg Faces recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Boiled eggs,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg,Low sugar,Sesame free,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Halloween Egg Faces Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bring a large saucepan of water to the boil. Add eggs, one at a time, and cook for 8 minutes. Drain and refresh under cold water.

When cool enough to handle, carefully peel eggs. Using a small sharp knife, cut a slice from the bottom of each egg to help it stand up, then cut out triangles for the eyes and mouths. Add capers to eye holes and sauce to mouth holes. Serve.
